node.text:
Giveaway!!! Over the past 10 years I have cruised the beaches documenting our amazing oceans to bring about environmental awareness!  @pacsafeofficial has been a brand by my side many of those years, constantly trying to do better for our planet! 
At Pacsafe we Protect What’s Valuable, and nothing is more valuable than the planet we travel and live on. We have therefore decided to give away a Venturesafe EXP45 Econyl backpack made from recycled fishing nets to one of you! To get a chance to get your hands on this recycled favorite we’d like to see how beautiful the world looks where you are. Let’s share the joy!

Want to enter? It’s easy:

1. Be sure you’re following @pacsafeofficial & @benjhicks
2. Be sure your account is public
3. Upload a picture and tag #ProtectWhatsValuable.

Giveaway closes Tuesday, August 23th, 2021 11:59pm PST. The winners will be announced on Friday, August 27th.
Winners need to get in touch via Instagram Message within three days, otherwise we will have to pick someone else - so keep your eyes peeled! This giveaway is in no way sponsored, endorsed, administered by, or associated with Instagram.

📷 : @juliarosephotog 

#ProtectWhatsValuable #ReduceOceanPlastic #pacsafe

node.text:
The old saying, “the best camera is the one that’s with you” has never been more true in modern times. My phone is always with me along with my housing for it. This is the newest @axisgo iPhone 12 Pro and Pro max housing that allows me to extend my quick run and gun shooting and sharing via my iPhone!  I have complete access to my touch screen and when shooting on the fly with the pistol it fires via Bluetooth, never missing a beat.  Pictured is also the dome port for split images.  I use my Aquatech 1dx2 housing for a lot of my work but this little guy can do an amazing job for what it is.  Thanks @aquatech_imagingsolutions and @axisgo for being part of the family. 
#iphone12pro #aquatech #axisgo #underwaterhousing #bluetooth
